TY  - JOUR
T1  - Maximizing Sequence-Submodular Functions and Its Application to Online Advertising
AU  - Alaei, Saeed
AU  - Makhdoumi, Ali
AU  - Malekian, Azarakhsh
Y1  - 2021/02/04
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2021/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2020.3820
